article_id:1034,category_name:News,title_name:Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!,image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1580094000"></span>]</strong></span><br>The issue where the displayed Might value did not increase after unlocking the &quot;Advanced Training&quot; node of the mana spiral was fixed in version 1.16.0, so the Might values displayed in this notification have been updated.<br>After updating to version 1.16.0, the Might value with 70 mana nodes unlocked will be as shown in this notification.<br>Note: Only the displayed Might value has changed. The power of standard attacks has not been changed.</div><hr><div><br></div><div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurers starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1579759200"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1580277600"></span>.<br><br>The adventurers affected this time and their stats are described below.<br><br>■Affected Adventurers<br>Added <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1579759200"></span>:<br>5★ Curran (shadow/axe)<br>5★ Heinwald (shadow/staff)<br>5★ Lathna (shadow/lance)<br>4★ Patia (shadow/lance)<br>Added <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1580277600"></span>:<br>5★ Delphi (shadow/dagger)</div><div><br></div><div>■Stats</div><div>・5★ adventurer</div><div>
